        "subject": "LU-6142 lov: don't use LARGE to alloc r0->lo_sub",
        "message": "LU-6142 lov: don't use LARGE to alloc r0->lo_sub\n\n->lo_sub is an array of pointers to slices in a RAID0\nand while it could be hundreds, or maybe thousands, it doesn't need a\nLARGE allocation.\n\nSo switch to a regular allocation.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Mr NeilBrown <neilb@suse.de>\nChange-Id: Ia8043b4259c656accdf7dcf71f3c711914d9d655\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
